      <title>Thrasio 申请破产法第 11 章以重组债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/thrasio-files-for-chapter-11-in-bid-to-restructure-its-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Thrasio Holdings Inc. 已根据美国破产法第 11 章申请破产保护，作为与贷方达成协议的一部分，旨在为其提供新资本并摆脱约 4.95 亿美元的债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/thrasio-files-for-chapter-11-in-bid-to-restructure-its-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 07:21:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
